snippet.title: March of the Drunken Sailors - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cosmic Spud proudly presents, March of the Drunken Sailors, which is now available!!!

Stop the sailors from getting to their boat to fish the seas. Unite and use the creatures of the sea to stop this from happening. Use physics to push and pull them off the dock before they can get there in this goofy physics based tower defense.

Now available!!!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2326500/March_of_the_Drunken_Sailors/
https://cosmic-spud.itch.io/march-of-the-drunken-sailors

Keep up to date on development and other news:
https://www.reddit.com/r/CosmicSpud/
https://twitter.com/CosmicSpud_devs
https://discord.gg/Ffuw8Y6qde

Music by Matthew Martino.
#MotDS
